title: 🎉 Annual dotnet/msbuild community survey 2023 🎉
body:
Hello everyone, we'd like to hear from you in this year's repo survey. Whether you open or comment on issues, or contribute PR's, please help this repo get better.

Here's the survey link -- you can complete it for up to 3 repos:
https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/8KTX9VT?Source=RepoLink

We've run this several years and it helps us find areas to improve and compare best practices across repos.
